# The curated reference-pack list (decision 144) — the assemblies the WASM playground ships so the
# UNCHANGED generator can resolve types and tag helpers in the browser. The list is DISCOVERED, not
# designed: playground/prove-refpack.sh runs the FULL generator test suite against a layout holding
# exactly these, and the suite being green is the equivalence proof. Add a name only when the proof
# demands it; every addition costs the visitor bytes.
